title: Sangean FM Stereo RDS/AM Portable Receiver PRD5 Overview
description:
Buy Sangean FM Stereo RDS/AM Portable Receiver - http://www.abt.com/resources/pages/search.php?keywords=prd5

Features:
• 200mm ferrite AM antenna bar to allow best AM reception
• 10 station presets (5 FM 5 AM)
• Easy to read LCD display with backlight
• PLL synthesized tuning system
• Excellent reception and stereo audio performance
• Stereo / Mono switch
• Auto seek station
• Alarm by radio or HWS (Humane Wake System) buzzer
• Sleep timer
• Battery power indicator
